label: fisheryInTheWild
definition: Fishery in the wild (including game fishing)

label: conservationOrWildlifeManagement
definition: Introduction for conservation purposes or wildlife management

label: releasedForUse
definition: Release in nature for use (other than above, e.g., fur, transport, medical use)

label: pet
definition: Pet/aquarium/terrarium species (including live food for such species )

label: farmedAnimals
definition: Farmed animals (including animals left under limited control)

label: contaminantOnAnimals
definition: Contaminant on animals (except parasites, species transported by host/vector)

label: parasitesOnAnimals
definition: Parasites on animals (including species transported by host and vector)

label: contaminantOnPlants
definition: Contaminant on plants (except parasites, species transported by host/vector)

label: parasitesOnPlants
definition: Parasites on plants (including species transported by host and vector)

label: hitchhikersShip
definition: Hitchhikers on ship/boat (excluding ballast water and hull fouling)

label: people
definition: People and their luggage/equipment (in particular tourism)

label: packingMaterial
definition: Organic packing material, in particular wood packaging
